{
  "stem": "10862.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had to pull all-- all six of us through that sickness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The death on the streets, every morning, where you get up, you'd find dead corpse on the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people were trying to take off their clothes, because they needed the clothes themselves for warmth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no dignity left anymore in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People became-- people that normally would smile at you, would be nice to you, became vicious, became very, very mean.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because all they were thinking about is themselves and how are they going to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was so bad in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, of course, everywhere you went, the Germans were there, you know, with the German-- the dogs, the German shepherds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember the hunger that I suffered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I used to come into the house, and my mother would say to me-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING] [SOBBING] she said to me, go out and play.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She said, if you will play and sing a song, you'll forget that you're hungry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother was only 39 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I turned 39 years old, when I was 39, and I remember going to services.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spoke to my rabbi that morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm 39 years old today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother was 39 when she was killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the biggest pain that I have is remembering when-- [CRYING] when she told me she cannot feed me, because she had no food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the pain, the pain she must have had to tell me, I have nothing to give you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You'll just have to go out and try to sing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe you'll forget how hungry you were.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
